headline: Palantir Gears Up to Report Q4 Earnings: What's in the Offing?
summary: PLTR heads into fourth-quarter earnings with revenues likely to be up 62.8% YoY as AI demand lifts government and commercial sales. EPS expected to rise 64.3%.
